                            <comment id="16443543" author="dsmiley" created="Thu, 19 Apr 2018 03:48:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I wasn&apos;t expecting this is in committable shape yet... I&apos;ll find out if this actually works over in the SolrTextTagger tests which has a test that posts plain text (not XML or JavaBin) to a custom RequestHandler. &#160;That&apos;s what prompted this issue (and another).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/OpenSextant/SolrTextTagger/blob/ab6951a1f77218f2b27ff00e9a13970fd70fffb3/src/test/java/org/opensextant/solrtexttagger/EmbeddedSolrNoSerializeTest.java#L106&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/OpenSextant/SolrTextTagger/blob/ab6951a1f77218f2b27ff00e9a13970fd70fffb3/src/test/java/org/opensextant/solrtexttagger/EmbeddedSolrNoSerializeTest.java#L106&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

